sub_title: Building connections and partnerships to speed up transitions in Food Systems, Water and Climate action
summary: I connect people to solve today's challenges in Food Systems, Water Management, Climate Change and our Living Environment. I've been managing and initiating both private and public organisations, programmes and projects in the Netherlands as well as in other countries and continents.
